Don, everything is connected somehow or else we can make it so.  lol   I don&#39;t know about eh EMF part but I do know that I am in an area of Mexico that get very few radio stations...that is except when it is about to storm.  I just noticed that a few weeks ago and will be ready with my RS hack for the next one.  Also, I recall that a few months ago one of our members had an actual EVP capture with the hack where the message was something to the effect that &quot;the Hack worked best when it was raining.&quot;  Now this may not have anything to do with your subject of EMF but WTF, there it is.    lol   ron l

